scroll-behavior: smooth; 

Css	Naming grid lines
	name to rows,cols
	
Css	Naming grid areas
	grid-template-areas
	grid-area

	every grid items has grid-area property with particular name.

	container -> grid-template-areas layout;

minmax();
	min-content,max-content
	rows/cols height/width -> change
	minmax(min,max);


Implicit Grid & Explicit Grid;
	explicit grid-we handle styling.
		
		automatically generated :implicite
		grid-auto-rows:50px;

		when we want implicite rows as cols;
		grid-auto-flow:column;
		grid-auto-columns:.5fr;

Alignments oF grid Items.
	
			justify-items:end|start|center|strecth;
			align-items:end|start|center|strecth;

			place-items:start end

			grid item ->
					justify-self,align-self,place-self

Alignments oF grid Tracks
	(All Grid)
	justify-content:start|end|center|stretch|space-around|space-between|space-evenly
	align-content:start|end|center|stretch|space-around|space-between|space-evenly
	place-content : align-content justify-content

